comments: Durant (BKN) places and quickly removes his right arm from the side of Winslow (POR) during the post up.
Claxton (BKN) and Watford (POR) engage and disengage during the rebounding opportunity.
Brown (BKN) legally contests the perimeter jump shot from Hart (POR).
Brown (BKN) makes brief marginal contact with the right arm of McLemore (POR) but the contact does not impact the latter's rebounding opportunity.
Curry (BKN) jumps behind Hart (POR) and does not make any contact during or after the perimeter jump shot attempt.
Durant (BKN) and Winslow (POR) engage away from the ball and the former's arms extend slightly during the disengage but the contact is marginal.
Durant (BKN) establishes himself in a wide screening position in the path of Williams (POR) but the contact on pick is marginal.
Watford (POR) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Dragic (BKN) is not in a legal guarding position when Hart's (POR) arm makes contact with the shoulder of Dragic that impacts the attempt at the rim.
Watford (POR) legally contests the driving shot attempt by Brown (BKN).
Hart (POR) rips through to start his drive and marginal arm contact occurs with Claxton (BKN) that does not impact Hart's SQBR.
Durant (BKN) and Winslow (POR) engage and disengage during the inbound play.
From all available angles, Hart's (POR) arm makes last contact with the ball prior to it bouncing out of bounds.
Hart (POR) moves into Brown's space and extends his right arm into the latter's body, which displaces the offensive player after receiving the ball.
Durant (BKN) comes off of the screen and moves into Hart's (POR) as the players engage and disengage during the inbound play.
Hart (POR) moves into Durant's (BKN) space and makes body contact that dislodges him after the latter receives the pass.
Watford's (POR) arms come out slightly and the contact to Claxton (BKN) is marginal as the player's disengage during the inbound play.
Claxton (BKN) legally contests the driving shot attempt from Williams (POR).
Durant's (BKN) extends outwards and some marginal contact occurs with Hart (POR) that does not affect his rebounding opportunity.
Williams (POR) chases Curry (BKN) during the inbound play and incidental foot to foot contact occurs between the two players.
Watford (POR) commits a take foul on Curry (BKN).
